message: Dear Bob, I am excited to offer you our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit you based on your needs and interests. Given its value to you, I propose a price of $9,500 for the product. This is a special offer tailored specifically for you, aiming to provide you with an excellent opportunity to acquire it without compromising your budget. Please let me know if this proposal meets your expectations or if there's any other way I can assist you in making your decision.
